collections.name: Haetty
collections.description:
Haetty – Your Adorable NFT Guardian Inspired by Haetae 🦁✨
What is Haetae?
Haetae (獬豸, Haetae) is a mythical guardian beast from Korean legends, known for protecting justice and preventing fires with its mystical powers.

Characteristics of Haetae
🦁 It has a lion-like body with a single horn on its forehead and is covered in scaly armor.
⚖️ With the ability to distinguish right from wrong, Haetae symbolizes justice and is widely used in Korea to represent law and order.
🔥 Its fire-preventing power made it a guardian of palaces and buildings, where stone statues of Haetae were placed to ward off disasters.

Even today, Haetae remains a beloved symbol of protection and justice. 🚀🔥

collections.name: San Giovanni di Sinis - Sardegna - Italia
collections.description: Ho scattato questa foto con la mia fidata Nikon D800, abbinata a un teleobiettivo Sigma 120-400mm, per catturare in primo piano l’atmosfera sospesa di San Giovanni di Sinis. Da quando ero bambino, questa torre e la brezza del mare mi ricordano le storie dei Fenici e le rovine di Tharros, luoghi che ho esplorato un milione di volte, col naso all’insù e gli occhi pieni di stupore. Il leggero velo di nebbia regala al paesaggio un senso di mistero e di intimità: sembra quasi di camminare tra la storia millenaria della costa sarda, con il mare che sussurra leggende antiche. L’uso del teleobiettivo ha compresso lo spazio, facendo emergere in modo quasi drammatico la sagoma della torre, circondata da un alone dorato. Ogni dettaglio, dal mare calmo al cielo velato, è un frammento di memoria che mi riporta alle mie radici, a quel legame indissolubile con la terra in cui sono nato.

collections.name: Geometric Harmonies - Javascript P5JS
collections.description:
Welcome to Geometric Harmonies, a collection of generative NFTs that blend art, music, and algorithms into a unique and immersive experience. Each piece is a visual and auditory symphony, created in real-time by code that reflects the beauty and complexity of the universe.

- Dynamic Generative Art: Geometric shapes dance across the screen, colliding, teleporting, and creating infinite patterns. Each movement is unique, guided by algorithms that simulate the causality and randomness of nature.
- Harmonic Generative Music: Accompanying the shapes, a generative soundtrack plays random chords in a harmonic scale. The music is created in real-time, ensuring each NFT has its own "sonic signature."
- Interactivity: By clicking on the screen, new shapes are added, creating an interactive and personalized experience. The NFT is not just a piece of art but a living experience.

Technology: Developed in JavaScript with p5.js and p5.sound.
Format: Interactive generative NFT.
Limited Edition: Each mint is unique, with an exclusive combination of shapes, colors, and sounds.

This NFT is more than a digital artwork; it is a sensory experience that combines hypnotic visuals, relaxing music, and interactivity. By acquiring this piece, you are owning a unique possibility of creations, generated by algorithms that reflect the harmony and complexity of the world around us, that is also a NON-REPEATABLE NFT, a non-repeatable experience.

Don’t miss the chance to own a piece of art that redefines the boundaries of digital creativity. Acquire your NFT today and become part of the generative art revolution!
